Google,Tasks,provides,a,to,do,list,system,for,users,within,GMail,Calendar,iGoogle,home,page,and,a,direct,mobile,site,The,Google,Tasks,API,provides,developers,with,a,set,of,API,endpoints,for,searching,reading,and,updating,Google,Tasks,content,and,metadata,With,the,API,a,user,can,retrieve,update,delete,and,create,task,lists,as,well,as,retrieve,update,order,delete,and,create,tasks,The,service,is,currently,in,Google,Labs,so,it,s,considered,to,be,in,beta,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON